title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Eddie's Walk from West Virginia down to Tennessee.  (Week of 6/21)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Eddie's Walk from West Virginia down to Tennessee.  (Week of 6/21)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 has on Eddie and Scuba Steve to recap all the things they didn't get to share on the show from their walk from West Virginia down to Tennessee.
